title: Spicy Beef Empanadas | Felicitas Pizarro
description:
Direct from Argentina, this fantastic empanada recipe is our first video from the winner of Food Tube's Search for a Star - the fabulous Felicitas! She shows you how to make the empanada dough from scratch as well as creating a gorgeous spicy dressing. Super delicious! More please Felicitas!

Check out her own channel and subscribe for more videos
http://goo.gl/9XU9Mw

What do you like in your empanadas? Let us know in the
comments box below.
